data.description: Welcome to this one-of-a-kind opportunity to own a delightful fixer-upper home that's bursting with character and possibilities. Located in a peaceful neighborhood, this property is perfect for those seeking a creative project to turn a diamond in the rough into a sparkling gem. It features 4 bedrooms 3.5 baths and a sparkling pool. This home presents an excellent chance for investors or DIY enthusiasts looking to add value through renovations and updates.
